OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain spreads
OL,6,Fnortheast through the evening, heavy
OL,7,Ffor a time. Becoming largely dry
OL,8,Fovernight with clear spells in the
OL,9,Feast, but cloudy with patchy light
OL,10,Frain in the west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FDry and warm with sunny
OL,13,Fspells in the east. Cooler in the west
OL,14,Fand cloudy to start but some bright
OL,15,Fspells developing during the day
OL,16,Fbefore some rain overnight. Windy.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,19,Fdry, warm and bright in the east from
OL,20,FSunday to Tuesday. Cooler and cloudier
OL,21,Fwith rain at times in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
